fr.lipn.uima.util.align
Interface SimpleTokenByLineReader.FilterTokenAndAnnot

Enclosing class:
SimpleTokenByLineReader
public static interface SimpleTokenByLineReader.FilterTokenAndAnnot

An object can implement this interface to filter special cases. Its methods are called in SimpleTokenByLineReader.processNextToken(InputReader, AlignerConsumer) before calling InputReader.receiveTokenAndAnnotation(AlignerConsumer, String, String), thus this object is able to remove/transform the token and annotation that were read.
